rows.label: tlk000016_msg0001
rows.name:
Dorara hear the news!
Friends wanting to go to Luxuria?

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0005
rows.name:
Actually, ship captain was Acedian, and
go into deep mourning for Fan-sama.
Then was nobody left to steer ship...

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0006
rows.name:
And so, Dorara get selected to replace!
Dorara never go there before, so will
have to work hard to make trip success!

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0007
rows.name:
Dorara not worry, though. With prince
of Luxuria on board, getting in should
be piece of pollen cake!

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0008
rows.name:
Dorara understand. Friends need
mental composure before visit
to Luxuria.

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0009
rows.name:
Dorara not going anywhere, so no need
for rushings!
